items.title: Sunpentown RF-322SS 3.2 cu. ft. Double Door Refrigerator with Energy Star
items.shelf_description:
If you're serious about snacking, then it's time you opened the Sunpentown RF-322SS 3.2 cu. ft. Double Door Refrigerator with Energy Star and discovered a whole new world of snack storage. Designed for use in dorm rooms, offices, or any other space where you might like a quick snack or drink, this deluxe refrigerator features separate fridge and freezer compartments. It sports an impressive 3.2 cubic feet of interior space and two reversible doors. The tall bottle rack, glass storage shelf, slide-out wire shelf, and transparent storage drawer combine to make this an ultra-roomy refrigerator. The flush-back design lets this fashionable fridge fit against any wall, while the leveling legs give you sturdy support on any surface. Bottom line: this deluxe double-door refrigerator is for serious snackers.

About Sunpentown Sunpentown International designs and manufactures small home appliances for convenient kitchen use. Sunpentown is the largest single producer of induction cooktops in the world, controlling over 70% of the domestic market. Aiming to stay at the forefront of induction technology, Sunpentown is proud to introduce a new line of uniquely competitive built-in and Wok induction cooktops to appeal to the increasingly global market of the 21st century.

  • Energy-efficient refrigerator with freezer compartment
  • Sleek stainless steel finish
  • Reversible door with interior slide-out wire storage shelf
  • Flush-back design, front-leveling legs and can dispenser
  • Transparent storage drawer and glass storage shelf
  • Dimensions: 18.8L x 19.5W x 33.6H in.
